## Installation

### Download from the App Store (iPhone and iPad)

1. Open the App Store on your iPhone or iPad.
2. Search for "PDF Creator - Multilingual" in the search bar.
3. Tap on the app icon in the search results.
4. On the app page, tap the "Get" or "Download" button.
5. Authenticate with your Apple ID, if prompted.
6. Wait for the app to download and install on your device.
7. Once installed, the app icon will appear on your home screen.

## Features

PDF Creator - Multilingual offers a range of features to create your PDF in 61 Languages. your all-in-one solution for a clutter-free and efficient document experience. 
Explore the following capabilities:

### PDF Creator

PDF Creator appears on the first page where you need to add your content manually or use paste option to paste your text in the box. Select the Language in the top menu. Use PDF settings to define your how your PDF should be created. Then, use Save as PDF option to save the PDF to the PDF Library.

### PDF Viewer

Utilize the PDF Viewer directly from our PDF Manager by simply clicking the listed PDF once. It will seamlessly transition to our fully equipped PDF Viewer with a share and print option. Additionally, you can employ the search bar to locate your desired PDF and open the PDF viewer. Each listed PDF file comes with a menu, allowing you to choose whether to delete the PDF or print or share it with others

